// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-3091 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: c0409713-72e1-52a0-a5a9-e9d836d801ec

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *ubuntu:12.04* OR ImageFileName = *ubuntu:14.04* OR ImageFileName = *ubuntu:14.10*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
